headline: Duck Creek Technologies Announces 2025 Partner of the Year Award Winners
summary: Duck Creek Technologies, the global intelligent solutions provider defining the future of property and casualty (P&C) and general insurance, today announced the winners of the company's third annual Partner of the Year Awards. Accenture, Cognizant, Microsoft, Next Level Solutions, Snowflake, and Xceedance were recipients of this year's Partner of the Year awards, which recognize the power of partnerships and their role in driving success across the P&C and general insurance ecosystem.

headline: The Resource Management Institute Launches its New Resource Management Academy
summary: The Resource Management Institute (RMI), part of Belcan, a Cognizant company, announced today the launch of the Resource Management Academy, a comprehensive training and certification platform designed to strengthen the skills of professionals responsible for planning, assigning, and optimizing work across services organizations.

headline: Amazon, Apple, Meta probed by Senate panel over H-1B visa hiring
summary: The debate over H-1B visas is heating up after President Trump imposed a $100,000 fee on new petitioners, citing “systemic abuse” of the program.
